title: I Almost Do (Taylor's Version)
description:
This is a fan favorite from the Red album, and some think it should have been a track 5. Some even argue that it's Taylor's best breakup song! She penned this beautiful song rather than reach out to the boy that broke her heart. Ana, Nick, Amy and Lacey dive deep in to this song!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There's lots of ways to contact us!
